<hw>nonextant</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>No longer existing; inaccessible
through loss or destruction.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><q>Its <qex>nonextant</qex> original was written on vellum</q>
